  "texts": [
    "In addition, the diverse combinations of modalities employed in emotion recognition, particularly the combination of audio-visual-text-physiological data, are promising but necessitate further exploration.",
    "While the text modality has lower coverage, its integration with other modalities, especially in the context of advanced conversational agents, should not be dismissed.Audio-visual modality combination is dominant in CMER systems.",
    "The accessibility of these modalities and the sophistication of their analysis techniques, thanks to the evolution of machine learning and computer vision, contribute to their widespread adoption in CMER.",
    "However, this observation also underlines a notable imbalance in the exploration of other modality combinations.",
    "In particular, the incorporation of text and physiological signals in CMER systems remains substantially under-researched."
